% This file solves the covariance-steering problem using iterative risk 
% allocation with distributionally robust state risk constraints. 
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
